			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Debug book, act 3, wyrm's crossing, circus of the last days. Go through the checkpoint, and popper is straight ahead and slightly to the right (he's next to stoney and boney, the married couple selling statues). To trigger the options to buy Dribbles' hand, go to the circus stage, 1,1,1, the dialogue, use killcombat, and then go back to popper. You can speak to him and notice he had dribbles hand, or you can even grab it from the chair next to him (which will automatically trigger a dialogue). "
				},
